Hi friends 👋🏻 I’m alive and well, just haven’t been posting much because this full time reselling is kicking my butt!
I have had some messages about if I’ll be coming back to YouTube anytime soon and that’s just such a hard question to answer right now since I love what I’m currently doing and taking up all my time. 
With that being said, I still want to hang out with all my friends so please come hang out with me on @whatnot ! Interacting in real time while slinging some vintage has been so much fun and I would love to continue growing our community! 
Thanks for those who reached out to check on me - love you all 🫶🏻✨

When you love your inventory too much so you just wear it till it sells >>>>>
Also I FINALLY hung up this incredible Disneyland sign in the house so I only thought this photo was appropriate.
In my match era and I’m not mad about it 🌿

I forgot how to do this whole Instagram thing but I wanted to show off my vintage raccoon tee because duh 🦝
In Atlanta for a few days and I already stopped at my first fav spot. Swipe for my amazing vegan matcha ice cream ✨
This is probably my favorite part of my apartment ✨ everything has been thrifted and can’t wait to keep adding to the collection 🥹 - fall decor is coming right up 🎃

Beautiful day + cute outfit + fall on the ground = pure bliss ✨🫶🏻
Got my hair cut (bangs are back!) , got an iced coffee and then walked around target and looked at every single 🎃👻 thing in those aisles. 
I feel I am my true self and thrive during this season. It just makes me so dang happy 🥹🫶🏻

Finally coming back with some thrift hauls because I missed doing them 🥹🫶🏻 how did I do?
